&nbsp;A man was found lying dead in the middle of the Indaba Lane in Muldersdrift on Wednesday.It is alleged that signs showed that the man had been dead long before he was found.According to ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring,the paramedics were dispatched to the scene aftersecurity guards found the naked body on the road.&#8220;Paramedics assessed the man and found that he had sustained a serious wound to his neck and showed no signs of life,unfortunately, nothing could be done for the man and he was declared dead on the scene&#8221;, Meiring said.While the cause of the incident remains unknown local authorities were on the scene to investigate further.-TNA Reporter&nbsp;